title: Dreamers-Thai
description:
Dreamers

Thai Movie. Starring Sornram Theppitak, Kulsatree Siriponggreeda & Anan Boonnark.

Love is an understanding each other or a lovers dream fulfilment. Love always
plays a trick, like as a love story of Pim(kulasatee Siripongprda). She 
determines to be the greatest superstar and Thana(Ravit Therdwong), A rich
man, encourages her to make that dream come true. Meanwhile she is still love
with Nai(Sornam Thephitak), a poor man who has always loved her. To choose her
dream, or true love? What shall it be!

no subs, sorry.

2003 film Thai audio, 118 minutes long.

Enjoy.
